      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="0"> crust by weight. It ranks 62nd in terms of abundance among the elements. </text>
      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">In seawater it is found in the form of bromide anions – B</text>
